- data_input = JST['helpers/data_input']

%h4 Personal Info
.helper-text Finally, we need you to create a password (of 8+ characters) to make sure that only you can access the personal data you've entered in this form. If you already have an account, go ahead and enter your existing login credentials.
!= data_input(field: "user.email", ctx: @ctx, span_width: 6)
!= data_input(field: "user.password", ctx: @ctx, span_width: 6, type: 'password')